text: Birgit Schielin (born March 22, 1979 in Vienna) is an Austrian rhythmic gymnast. Schielin competed for Austria in the rhythmic gymnastics individual all-around competition at the 1996 Summer Olympics in Atlanta. There she was 24th in the qualification round and did not advance to the semifinal. == References == == External links == * * Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian rhythmic gymnasts Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic gymnasts of Austria Category:Sportspeople from Vienna
